  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Crazy Golf Party Is a new and exciting golf game that tries to take the original format of crazy golf and bring it into game format in new and exciting ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras/1b8dd330a6b2c10b8cdadb705b51bcf4.avif?t=1763066904\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras_big/1b8dd330a6b2c10b8cdadb705b51bcf4.avif?t=1763066904 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit Our Official Discord For Crusade Developments where you can suggest and give feedback on crazy golf party! (Link In Info Section)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Features:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutliplayer!</strong> The game features 15 player coop that can be played Online or Lan with you, your friends and family to see who is the best golfer of all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras/6e63e43c992eb371cc890ecdbf364642.avif?t=1763066904\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras_big/6e63e43c992eb371cc890ecdbf364642.avif?t=1763066904 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Customisation!</strong> There is a variety of hats and skins that you can customise your golf ball to look any way you want from Cool to Goofy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras/15fe970532e63928924a0f69aff4b889.avif?t=1763066904\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras_big/15fe970532e63928924a0f69aff4b889.avif?t=1763066904 width=800 height=358 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 5 Exciting Maps To Discover On Release!</strong> We have 5 maps on release, the maps releasing are Funderheim, Elden Forest, Egypt, Windmill Valley & Haunted Hallows!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras/34187aa1018f50fa43e16022818e41f7.avif?t=1763066904\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras_big/34187aa1018f50fa43e16022818e41f7.avif?t=1763066904 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Themed Maps!</strong> Each map in unique and themed so that there is a map for everyone From Egypt to forests filled with strange magic! And Maybe In the Future Maybe To The Sea To Plunder And Pillage?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras/3a1874ac63106af038c8229e18a5996c.avif?t=1763066904\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524060/extras_big/3a1874ac63106af038c8229e18a5996c.avif?t=1763066904 width=800 height=398 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
